    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and documented; the overall body of evidence — including multi-laboratory experimental comparison, E/uval values well below 1.96 for all QoIs, and full input traceability — supports acceptance of the FEA framework for the stated COU. The statistical validation methodology referenced in the computational methods literature (referencesIdentifier: https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ymeth.2024.03.003) underpins the E/uval calculation approach adopted here.",
